full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/13/2023 2RS PINDIA'S ENT ET WORLD TWO RUPEES HIRE TWO RUPEES AFFIDAVIT I, Hari Ramchandra Gokhale, son of Shri SECURITY * Ramchandra Hari Gokhale, formerly Judge of the Bombay High Court, and now a Senior Advocate of the Supreme Court of India, living at C-109, Delhi South Extension Part II, New Delhi (India), solemnly affirm and declare as under :- That I was born on 5th October, 1915, at Baroda (India). I am uncle of Vishwanath Vinayak Phatak. I was present at the marriage of my sister, Vimala Ramchandra Gokhale to Vinayak Govind Phatak on March 4, 1926, at Baroda (India). Vishwanath Vinayak Phatak was born to Vinayak Govind Phatak and Vimala Vinayak Phatak on July 9, 1936, at the Sayaji General Hospital, Baroda (India). (H. R.
